data.title: Prime Video: Christina Milian Turned Up Season 2
data.meta_description: Actress, pop star and mother Christina Milian is constantly on the go - from AM to PM. Can she find contentment amongst the chaos?
data.text:
Christina kicks her career into high gear with her new music video, but Carmen feels excluded. Meanwhile, Lizzy has found a new calling and a new man!

Christina hears news that puts her relationship in jeopardy. Lizzy's plans for Dom's birthday end in disaster, while Richard lashes out at his in-laws.

Christina mentors a young girl band, only to find they may not be ready for the big time. Richard pursues his dreams of becoming a professional stuntman.

Christina repairs the damage between Ceraadi and Silent Killers. Meanwhile, Danielle tells Dom something that makes him question his future with Lizzy.

Christina invites Ceraadi to perform with her at The Rose Bowl but their lack of commitment makes her question their dedication.

Christina opens up about being a victim of domestic abuse while Dom attempts to make peace with Richard and Lizzy encroaches on Danielle's infomercial gig.

Christina preps for the opening of her WE ARE POP CULTURE clothing store, and worries that her â€œteam" won't get it together in time.

The countdown to Christina's boutique opening is on! Elsewhere, Dom leaves for France and Danielle's relationship continues to deteriorate.
